Class ConversationElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • adept.common.ConversationElement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasConversationElementTagAttributes, HasFreeTextAttributes, HasOntologizedAttributes, IConversationElementEntityRelation, IConversationElementRelation

    public class ConversationElement
extends Object
implements HasOntologizedAttributes, HasFreeTextAttributes, HasConversationElementTagAttributes, IConversationElementRelation, IConversationElementEntityRelation
    The Class ConversationElement, which represents the units of Conversation. For example, a single message in an email thread, or a single post in a discussion forum thread.
